33
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:44,070
别扭  什么意思
Weird? What do you mean?

34
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:49,060
我在厕所里看到你了  那么看着我
I saw you in the bathroom... looking at me.

35
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,410
不是第一次了
It's not the first time.

36
