因为完全无法保证这条路会通往何方
because we had no guarantee where it was going to lead us.

48
00:05:47,940 --> 00:05:50,730
那需要莫大的勇气
It took a steel goddamn stomach,

49
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:53,640
自此之后我们不得不做的一切都是如此
and so has everything else we had to do since.

50
00:05:56,210 --> 00:05:59,300
所以现在别去担心你和我
So don't worry about you and me now.

51
00:06:01,290 --> 00:06:03,050
找到你的勇气  克莱尔
Find your steel, Claire.

52
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:26,620
感谢大家前来
Thank you all very much for coming.

53
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:28,030
你看到这个了吗
Have you seen this?

54
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:35,240
{\an8}哈里发国占领了库尔德要塞

55
00:06:32,210 --> 00:06:35,690
哈里发国  哈里发帝国组织
ICO. Islamic Caliphate Organization.

56
00:06:35,930 --> 00:06:38,160
领袖是阿赫麦德和尤瑟夫·艾哈迈德
Ahmed and Yusuf Al Ahmadi.

57
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:40,210
他们一直精明地分开行动
They've been smart about keeping split up.

58
00:06:40,210 --> 00:06:42,080
万一一个死了  另一个就接管
If one dies, the other takes over.

59
00:06:42,090 --> 00:06:44,410
但他们要在北叙利亚召开策划会议
But they're holding a planning session in northern Syria.

60
00:06:44,410 --> 00:06:45,660
现在两人都在那里
Both are there right now.

61
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:47,710
我在约旦河谷被收拾得很惨
I got my ass handed to me over the Jordan Valley.

62
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:49,740
我不能批准发动导弹袭击
I'm not gonna launch a missile strike

63
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,390
除非我相信国家安全
unless I believe that there's an overwhelming

64
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:52,480
严重受到威胁
national security threat,

65
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:55,000
而我不认为他们构成这种威胁
and I'm just not convinced that they pose one.

66
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,670
总统认为哈里发国是严重威胁
The president believes ICO to be a serious threat.

67
00:06:57,670 --> 00:07:01,140
我们认为他们在积极地招募美国民众
We believe they are actively recruiting American citizens.

68
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:03,000
因此  政府申请进行
Accordingly, the government is requesting

69
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:06,470
702章逆向监听令
a Section 702 upstream surveillance order.

70
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:10,680
-国内监控  -监控流量  不是个人
- Domestic surveillance. - Monitoring traffic, not individuals.

71
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,420
上前
Approach the bench.

72
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,660
外国情报监视法法庭  机密判决的闭门的
The FISA Court. Classified rulings behind closed doors.

73
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:18,310
就连他们都不知道我们今早派去了律师
Not even these men know we have a lawyer in there this morning.

74
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:21,090
哈里发国已经控制了三个油田
ICO already has three oil fields under their control.

75
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,710
俄国减产时
They made a fortune selling crude

76
00:07:22,710 --> 00:07:24,300
他们靠卖原油大挣了一笔
