98
00:08:23,130 --> 00:08:26,550
这把枪打死了鲍勃和苏·格兰特14岁的儿子
This gun killed Bob and Sue Grant's 14-year-old son.

99
00:08:29,670 --> 00:08:34,190
这是打死了艾德华·密查姆特工的那把枪
And this is the gun that killed Agent Edward Meechum.

100
00:08:34,190 --> 00:08:38,210
{\an8}艾德华·H·密查姆

101
00:08:34,430 --> 00:08:37,620
没几个特勤局特工能葬在阿林顿国家公墓
Not many Secret Service agents buried at Arlington.

102
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:40,160
我认为这是他应得的
I'd say he earned his place.

103
00:08:40,630 --> 00:08:43,800
我没有意识到  他对我是多么重要
I took it for granted, how important he was to me,

104
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:45,590
我多么依赖他
how much I leaned on him.

105
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:49,400
现在他死了  我才看明白
It's clear to me now, now that he's gone.

106
00:08:52,530 --> 00:08:55,190
我不想对你犯同样的错误  唐纳德
I don't wanna make the same mistake with you, Donald.

107
00:08:55,300 --> 00:08:56,230
什么意思
How do you mean?

108
00:08:56,770 --> 00:08:59,640
我之前没意识到我多么倚重你
I didn't realize how much I lean on you.

109
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:03,280
