137
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:06,490
我们或许该联系一下领导层
Well, we should probably reach out to the leadership,

138
00:11:06,490 --> 00:11:08,100
询问他们的意见
and get their advice.

139
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:10,170
但你是对的
But you're right.

140
00:11:10,970 --> 00:11:15,030
不管是谁  得是一个对此十分渴求的人
Whoever it is, they need to be hungry for it.

141
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:18,220
这些死亡本都可以避免
All of these deaths could have been prevented.

142
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:19,300
因此
And that's why

143
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:22,380
我在跟一个参议员联盟合作  出台一部法律
I'm working with a coalition of senators to introduce a law

144
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:26,050
对所有枪支交易都进行背景审查
that will extend background checks to all gun transactions,

145
00:11:26,150 --> 00:11:28,550
包括枪支展和在线销售
including gun shows and online sales.

146
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:31,550
我想说清楚  这不是针对枪支持有的打击
And let me be clear, this is not an assault on gun ownership.

147
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:34,610
而是对非法持有枪支的打击
It's an assault on illegal gun ownership.

148
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,440
我现在将回答问题
I'll now take questions.

149
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:41,560
有请下任美国总统
The next President of the United States,

150
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:44,970
我的挚爱  一个母亲最好的伴侣
the love of my life, the best father a mother could hope for,

151
